main event: Three objects in a cluster were sighted from the ground at Keesler AFB, Mississippi and identified as large balloons tied together.
interesting points: The objects were observed moving towards the east at 60 knots,They were detected on ground radar,The report included multiple local sightings of the same objects,An F-86 aircraft reported seeing the objects at a high altitude over Dauphin Island,The balloons appeared to be extremely large as they looked like the size of a dime when close to the base.
witness description: base operations officer, UFO investigator, local pilots
